## 🛠️ Manual API Testing

### Send Single Telemetry:
```powershell
$body = @{
	deviceId = "device-001"
	metric = "temperature"
	value = 23.5
} | ConvertTo-Json

Invoke-RestMethod -Uri "http://localhost:5297/api/telemetry" -Method Post -Body $body -ContentType "application/json"
```

### Query Telemetry:
```powershell
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri "http://localhost:5297/api/telemetry?deviceId=device-001&metric=temperature"
```

